name: Laura Lux
description:
Laura Lux is an Australian Instagram model living in Texas. She also goes by the handle 'Very Big Milktank' and honestly I have no clue why.

The embed has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models. When rendering full body images I recommend using inpainting. She has a lot of tattoos and this can mess up results, but this can be mended with inpainting. For those of us less charmed by tattoos, v1.1 is now available. It produces tattoos much less often than v1.0 even without any negative input on tattoos, but I still recommend adding "tattoo, tattoos, tattood" in the negative prompts.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)

modelVersions.name: v1.1 - AntiTattoo
modelVersions.description:
After some feedback from Zidooqi9 I took a second look at the prominence of tattoos in the embedding.

This version should be noticably less eager to generate tattoos. While I recommend still adding "tattoo, tattoos, tattood" to the negative prompt, a much smaller portion of my batches now generate tattoos without asking for it, even if you don't tell the negative prompt about them.
